持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4497, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 437058, "username": "catning", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/catning", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75c8/2e17/437058_mini.png?m=1568193512", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75c8/2e17/437058_normal.png?m=1568193512", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75c8/2e17/437058_large.png?m=1568193512", "created": 1566291609, "last_modified": 1568193512, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Aspx", "last_touched": 1783095799, "title": "赛格那件事有后续了，但是我有点理解不了舆论", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224739", "created": 1783054039, "deleted": 0, "content": "上下文帖子： https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224349\r\n赛格公告： https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/iKLKHV7KaW3QlQg1Je-hNg\r\n\r\n昨天我就觉得疑点很多，顺手多搜了下：\r\n   1. 出事的不是所谓的小人物，运动品牌地区代理，手握好多品牌，几百家门店，流水几十亿。\r\n      -- 这种体量的人为什么被 1000w+ 的罚款搞死了，罚款是根因，还是压死骆驼的稻草。今天公告也说，提到他本身公司经营不善了。\r\n   2. 为什么只罚他，并且金额这么巨大，他到底套现了多少，让商场这么罚款。\r\n      -- 今天公告里说了相关的，但是没正面回复。合同说明了不能拆单去用，他们还用券帮外地经销商拿货，我觉得这个行为过分了，但是你经商，要赚黑钱，就要有心理去承受这罚款。\r\n\r\n大部分网友们的反应是：\r\n\t赛格未出公告前：资本逼死小人物。\r\n\t赛格出公告后：你信赛格的公告还是信我是秦始皇，这都是资本的手段，资本可真厉害啊。\r\n    \r\n我不是给商场开脱，我也没全信商场的发言，况且我觉得商场也有好多信息没解释，比如有没有让强制退场等。\r\n我只是觉得这件事疑点太多了，但是舆论关注点大部分都是资本搞死小人物的叙事上，什么都不去想，什么也听不进去。", "content_rendered": "上下文帖子： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224349\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224349</a><br />赛格公告： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/iKLKHV7KaW3QlQg1Je-hNg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/iKLKHV7KaW3QlQg1Je-hNg</a><br /><br />昨天我就觉得疑点很多，顺手多搜了下：<br />   1. 出事的不是所谓的小人物，运动品牌地区代理，手握好多品牌，几百家门店，流水几十亿。<br />      -- 这种体量的人为什么被 1000w+ 的罚款搞死了，罚款是根因，还是压死骆驼的稻草。今天公告也说，提到他本身公司经营不善了。<br />   2. 为什么只罚他，并且金额这么巨大，他到底套现了多少，让商场这么罚款。<br />      -- 今天公告里说了相关的，但是没正面回复。合同说明了不能拆单去用，他们还用券帮外地经销商拿货，我觉得这个行为过分了，但是你经商，要赚黑钱，就要有心理去承受这罚款。<br /><br />大部分网友们的反应是：<br />\t赛格未出公告前：资本逼死小人物。<br />\t赛格出公告后：你信赛格的公告还是信我是秦始皇，这都是资本的手段，资本可真厉害啊。<br />    <br />我不是给商场开脱，我也没全信商场的发言，况且我觉得商场也有好多信息没解释，比如有没有让强制退场等。<br />我只是觉得这件事疑点太多了，但是舆论关注点大部分都是资本搞死小人物的叙事上，什么都不去想，什么也听不进去。", "last_modified": 1783054369, "replies": 45, "id": 1224739}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239658, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4497, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 623288, "username": "Y25tIGxpdmlk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Y25tIGxpdmlk", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f59b786fd9cd2ec2b95720531ebbe83?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f59b786fd9cd2ec2b95720531ebbe83?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f59b786fd9cd2ec2b95720531ebbe83?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1681019214, "last_modified": 1716984949, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Ericcccccccc", "last_touched": 1783139097, "title": "暗色模式到底是怎么流行起来的？？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224886", "created": 1783131113, "deleted": 0, "content": "RT ，现在基本上但凡 IT 数码沾点边的站点或者软件，进去默认都是夜间模式、暗色模式。\r\n作为一个讨厌暗色模式的人，每次进去都要找半天日渐模式按钮在哪里，有些在右上角或者左下角直接可以切换的还好。\r\n有些 TM 的直接没有切换按钮或者藏在设置页深处的，简直想打人。\r\n\r\n夜间模式到底好在哪里啊？护眼吗？好像没有科学依据证明啊。\r\n日间模式看着多舒服啊，各种设计颜色都是原始的，夜间模式好多界面颜色啥的设计都变乱了，很丑啊。", "content_rendered": "RT ，现在基本上但凡 IT 数码沾点边的站点或者软件，进去默认都是夜间模式、暗色模式。<br />作为一个讨厌暗色模式的人，每次进去都要找半天日渐模式按钮在哪里，有些在右上角或者左下角直接可以切换的还好。<br />有些 TM 的直接没有切换按钮或者藏在设置页深处的，简直想打人。<br /><br />夜间模式到底好在哪里啊？护眼吗？好像没有科学依据证明啊。<br />日间模式看着多舒服啊，各种设计颜色都是原始的，夜间模式好多界面颜色啥的设计都变乱了，很丑啊。", "last_modified": 1783131113, "replies": 43, "id": 1224886}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 30828, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3325, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 406395, "username": "xxw1754352621", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xxw1754352621", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_mini.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_normal.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_large.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_xlarge.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_xxlarge.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_xxxlarge.png?m=1773115604", "created": 1556249871, "last_modified": 1773115604, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "msdurex", "last_touched": 1783136104, "title": "因为帮朋友代充了 ChatGPT Plus，我的 Apple ID 不干净了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224834", "created": 1783078610, "deleted": 0, "content": "起因是前几个月，我用我的美区 Apple Id ，帮我朋友代充了 ChatGPT Plus ，后面这个订阅过期了。\r\n\r\n后来我朋友用自己注册的美区 Apple Id 给自己的 ChatGPT 充值了。\r\n\r\n我最近由于工作需要使用 Codex ，准备自己充一波，钱扣了，然后提示什么错误，发现没有充上。\r\n\r\n点击恢复购买，提示 “你的 AppleID 购买项目关联到另一个 ChatGPT 账号。巴拉巴拉...”。\r\n\r\n后面跟我朋友联系，发现充到他的账号上了。并且是覆盖式的，他在 6 月 30 号充值的，我今天 7 月 3 号 充值的。他的 ChatGPT 账号显示 8 月 3 号过期...\r\n\r\n后来翻阅相关文档，发现是永久绑定的，天塌了！这个美区 Apple ID 是我长期使用的...以前真不知道，还有这样的操作", "content_rendered": "<p>起因是前几个月，我用我的美区 Apple Id ，帮我朋友代充了 ChatGPT Plus ，后面这个订阅过期了。</p>\n<p>后来我朋友用自己注册的美区 Apple Id 给自己的 ChatGPT 充值了。</p>\n<p>我最近由于工作需要使用 Codex ，准备自己充一波，钱扣了，然后提示什么错误，发现没有充上。</p>\n<p>点击恢复购买，提示 “你的 AppleID 购买项目关联到另一个 ChatGPT 账号。巴拉巴拉...”。</p>\n<p>后面跟我朋友联系，发现充到他的账号上了。并且是覆盖式的，他在 6 月 30 号充值的，我今天 7 月 3 号 充值的。他的 ChatGPT 账号显示 8 月 3 号过期...</p>\n<p>后来翻阅相关文档，发现是永久绑定的，天塌了！这个美区 Apple ID 是我长期使用的...以前真不知道，还有这样的操作</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783078610, "replies": 36, "id": 1224834}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/735b/90b4/67_large.png?m=1706750053", "name": "taste", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/735b/90b4/67_normal.png?m=1706750053", "title": "美酒与美食", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/taste", "topics": 874, "footer": "", "header": "关于那些好喝和好吃的", "title_alternative": "Taste", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/735b/90b4/67_mini.png?m=1706750053", "stars": 843, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 67, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 554904, "username": "11000111010", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/11000111010", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2849eb464101d4e008226d658410ce10?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2849eb464101d4e008226d658410ce10?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2849eb464101d4e008226d658410ce10?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1630486935, "last_modified": 1753324501, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "goumadantui", "last_touched": 1783106668, "title": "咸粽子好吃还是甜粽子好吃？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224812", "created": 1783071150, "deleted": 0, "content": "本人经常吃甜粽子，感觉甜粽子好吃，但是上一个端午节 朋友从南方寄过来几个咸粽子，有叉烧肉咸蛋黄的，有腊肉的还有一个是包的鲜肉粽。感觉都能接受呢？（把币扔给我🤣）", "content_rendered": "本人经常吃甜粽子，感觉甜粽子好吃，但是上一个端午节 朋友从南方寄过来几个咸粽子，有叉烧肉咸蛋黄的，有腊肉的还有一个是包的鲜肉粽。感觉都能接受呢？（把币扔给我🤣）", "last_modified": 1783128791, "replies": 33, "id": 1224812}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11172, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2379, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 410741, "username": "loving29cn", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/loving29cn", "website": "https://www.lajiaohttp.com?kwd=hyj-v2ex", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_mini.png?m=1782264977", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_normal.png?m=1782264977", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_large.png?m=1782264977", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_xlarge.png?m=1782264977", "created": 1557396422, "last_modified": 1782264977, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ethusdt", "last_touched": 1783105615, "title": "求一个好用的蓝牙耳机推荐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224791", "created": 1783068136, "deleted": 0, "content": "来个不要那么贵的，便宜一点的，质量还可以的，没有运动什么的需求，就平时听听歌，没有噪音，不会断连就行，续航差不多就行，我丢的就剩充电舱了，有线耳机又很容易缠绕，求一个大家用的趁手的", "content_rendered": "<p>来个不要那么贵的，便宜一点的，质量还可以的，没有运动什么的需求，就平时听听歌，没有噪音，不会断连就行，续航差不多就行，我丢的就剩充电舱了，有线耳机又很容易缠绕，求一个大家用的趁手的</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783068136, "replies": 31, "id": 1224791}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71871, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9720, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 235515, "username": "fansmaster", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fansmaster", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a657/bc40/235515_mini.png?m=1742437032", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a657/bc40/235515_normal.png?m=1742437032", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a657/bc40/235515_large.png?m=1742437032", "created": 1497432809, "last_modified": 1742437032, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "TIDS", "last_touched": 1783097787, "title": "做海外模型的 API 中转站，会被判刑吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224797", "created": 1783068870, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260629A07O8W00\r\n\r\n看了这个新闻，感觉有点虚啊，别钱没赚到，人进去了，有没有比较了解相关法律的给说说", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260629A07O8W00\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260629A07O8W00</a></p>\n<p>看了这个新闻，感觉有点虚啊，别钱没赚到，人进去了，有没有比较了解相关法律的给说说</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783068870, "replies": 26, "id": 1224797}]